{"word":"συμπληρόω","slug":"συμπληρόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συμπληρόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πληρόω\">πληρόω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘fill up completely’, in blend of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> and a boat exposed to onslaught of waves, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>be swamped <a href='B:490 8:23'>Lk 8:23</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of the idea of filling up, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> temporal focus: ‘take place’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> approach <a href='B:490 9:51'>Lk 9:51</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> be in progress <a href='B:510 2:1'>Ac 2:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συμπίπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συμπνίγω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}